OL,3,C'You're not alone here' - women share
OL,4,Cstories of migration through
OL,5,Cperformance
OL,7,FA musician is sharing the experiences
OL,8,Fof migrant women who have travelled to
OL,9,FBristol from all over the world
OL,10,Fthrough a performance.
OL,12,FThe project is a result of workshops
OL,13,Fwith a group of 15 South Asian, East
OL,14,FAsian, African, Middle Eastern, South
OL,15,FAmerican, Jewish, Irish, and refugee
OL,16,Fwomen.
OL,18,FOne of those stories belongs to
OL,19,FSherien Elsheikh who fled from Sudan
OL,20,Fto Bristol in 2008, when she was just
OL,21,F21 years old.
