OL,3,C'You're not alone here' - women share
OL,4,Cstories of migration through
OL,5,Cperformance
OL,7,FNow, 16 years later not only does she
OL,8,Fdescribe Bristol as her home but helps
OL,9,Fother refugees following in her
OL,10,Ffootsteps.
OL,12,FSherien explained: "Everything new for
OL,13,Fme, young person knowing nothing about
OL,14,Fthe country, a little bit sad because
OL,15,FI left my family from the beginning,
OL,16,FI've never been away from them.
