OL,3,C'You're not alone here' - women share
OL,4,Cstories of migration through
OL,5,Cperformance
OL,7,F"I love to help people and take them
OL,8,Ffrom their isolation as well and send
OL,9,Fthat feeling for them. You're not
OL,10,Falone here - we're all together, we
OL,11,Fhelp each other."
OL,13,F"This is my country now, that's what I
OL,14,Ffeel. This is my place my kids grow
OL,15,Fhere, born here, this is their
OL,16,Fcountry."
OL,18,F"For myself, I have found myself in
OL,19,Fthis project as well - I feel like
OL,20,Fwhen I talk about memory I just smile
OL,21,Fon my face."
