OL,3,C'You're not alone here' - women share
OL,4,Cstories of migration through
OL,5,Cperformance
OL,7,FSherien's is just one of several
OL,8,Fstories being told through music and
OL,9,Fspoken word.
OL,11,FThe project was created by Daphna
OL,12,FSadeh-Neu, who wanted to offer a
OL,13,Fplatform for women's voices.
OL,15,FDaphna said: "It was important for me
OL,16,Fto bring women's voices and subjects
OL,17,Flike unity, diversity, tolerance, and
OL,18,Funderstanding, as we have so much
OL,19,Fseparation in our world now and
OL,20,Fwomen's voices are not always heard.
