OL,7,F"So it was important to me to project
OL,8,Fthat through the arts and through real
OL,9,Fstories."
OL,11,F15 women from different backgrounds
OL,12,Fhave contributed to the project,
OL,13,Fincluding Valerie Russell Emmott.
OL,15,FValerie said: "So I'm Jewish, I had a
OL,16,FJewish mum and a Christian dad and one
OL,17,Fyear when I was just really wondering
OL,18,Fabout how I would be treated if I
OL,19,Fopenly told everybody I came across
OL,20,Fthat I was Jewish, I did an experiment.
