OL,3,C'You're not alone here' - women share
OL,4,Cstories of migration through
OL,5,Cperformance
OL,7,F"I put on the Star of David necklace
OL,8,Fit was quite sizeable, couldn't really
OL,9,Fmiss it and went on the bus to work,
OL,10,Fcommuted to and from the workplace, I
OL,11,Fwore it in all my meetings in the
OL,12,Fworkplace, I wore it when I got home
OL,13,Fand nothing happened - thank god.
OL,15,F"I didn't get mugged I didn't get
OL,16,Fhassled, no one gave me a hard time. I
OL,17,Fthink we're more accepting. I hope
OL,18,Fwe're a more accepting culture now
OL,19,Fabout people's gender identities,
OL,20,Fpeople's sexual identities, and
OL,21,Fpeople's religions and beliefs."
