OL,7,FSinger Nia Bimkubwa said that
OL,8,Fcontributors and creatives value being
OL,9,Fpart of the experience, creating that
OL,10,Fsafe space to be able to open up and
OL,11,Fshare with others.
OL,13,FForgotten Songs and Stories in
OL,14,Fcollaboration with Global Majority
OL,15,Fwomen in Bristol is funded by Arts
OL,16,FCouncil England.
OL,18,FIt debuts on Wednesday 31 January at
OL,19,Fthe Bristol Beacon.
